HEADWORD: Anthodium
<hw>An*tho"di*um</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., from
Gr. <?/ like flowers, flowery; <grk>'a`nqos</grk> flower +
<grk>e'i^dos</grk> form.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The inflorescence
